232
0:12:57.16,000 --> 0:12:59,000
que j'ai emprunté,

233
0:12:59.16,000 --> 0:13:,000
(Rires)

234
0:13:00.16,000 --> 0:13:02,000
à un ami.

235
0:13:02.16,000 --> 0:13:03,000
